{"tid":2381962,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"又講下PS5個OX其實係幾咁on9","createTime":"2021-01-27T03:23:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-27T10:11:32.000Z","uid":123926,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"9181decef7bc6c34684dc2a592fd2dacf686b26c","tid":2381962,"uid":123926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T03:23:57.000Z","msg":"見隔離講開就分享一下,<br />\nSony自稱係為左統一免混亂, 所以 O=取消, X=確認,<br />\n現階段其實玩返好多舊game反而係更加混亂,<br />\n有好多操作變左無限循環<br />\n舉2個例子: 以下藍字為PS4, 紅字為 PS5 <br />\n<strong>1, 芒亨世界 </strong><br />\n確定<span class=\"blue\">O</span> <span class=\"red\">X</span><br />\n取消<span class=\"blue\">X</span> <span class=\"red\">O</span><br />\n同 NPC 講野 <span class=\"blue\">O</span> <span class=\"red\">X</span><br />\n執石仔, 執道具, 上翼龍移動, 搬炮彈, 開炮(戰場上嘅大型武器), 開閘<span class=\"blue\">O</span> <span class=\"red\">O</span><br />\n入 camp  <span class=\"blue\">O</span> <span class=\"red\">X</span><br />\n<em>由呢度睇到, PS4 喺戰場上嘅操作全部都係統一左喺O, <br />\nO 係非攻擊狀態時係無任何動作嘅<br />\nPS5 唯獨是將入 camp 改喺 X, 而 X 預設係翻滾, <br />\n即係如果太早按的話, 會見到個角色 on99 咁喺個 camp 前面碌黎碌去,<br />\nPS4 就無呢個問題</em><br />\n<br />\n望遠鏡 &gt; 取消望遠鏡 <span class=\"blue\">X</span> <span class=\"red\">X</span> <br />\n望遠鏡 &gt; 觀察報告 <span class=\"blue\">O</span> <span class=\"red\">O</span> <br />\n退出觀察報告<span class=\"blue\">X</span> <span class=\"red\">O</span><br />\nPS5 呢度變左一個無限循環<br />\n入觀察報告 <span class=\"red\">O</span> &gt; 退出觀察報告 <span class=\"red\">O</span> &gt; 入觀察報告 <span class=\"red\">O</span> ....<br />\n<br />\n<strong>2, 戰神</strong><br />\n因為係 PS5 送嘅, 所以無玩過 PS4 版,<br />\n基本上一樣係取消<span class=\"blue\">X</span> <span class=\"red\">O</span><br />\nO 同芒亨一樣係執野, 開寶箱等操作<br />\n所以傳送門嘅操作就出現左一個無限循環,<br />\n開啓傳送門 <span class=\"red\">O</span> &gt; 退出傳送門 <span class=\"red\">O</span> &gt;開啓傳送門 <span class=\"red\">O</span> &hellip;<br />\n<br />\n以上只係玩左 2隻驚發現到嘅問題,<br />\n其他應該仲有好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ab57f1524599ab83f0c883a7da80797a7675991","tid":2381962,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T03:26:24.000Z","msg":"ps4有得揀 x as enter <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0eb93937f98e60f0543284601856ed2894c0c3c","tid":2381962,"uid":8902,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T03:31:42.000Z","msg":"用ps5玩刺客維京，會變返O確定X取消<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85dfd19bd9239178f818a3d3c710de711a9cd7b7","tid":2381962,"uid":114196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T03:40:01.000Z","msg":"精神錯亂系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9afa4ead2a085eb1cd4c8de95db58ce29042f6e","tid":2381962,"uid":98713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ab57f1524599ab83f0c883a7da80797a7675991","tid":2381962,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T03:26:24.000Z","msg":"ps4有得揀 x as enter <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T03:40:43.000Z","msg":"有D GAME冇咩用<br />\n好似人中個類你轉完佢都係O係確認"},{"pid":"f40b14d551c285e0cf12d1796661424a87c41edc","tid":2381962,"uid":24311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T03:54:02.000Z","msg":"仁王2都係<br />\n撳O同NPC傾完 之後要撳X揀確定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3af669d0ca9c5349a1b95106ddd3b2cc9ea534d4","tid":2381962,"uid":90259,"like":6,"dislike":7,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T04:44:04.000Z","msg":"冇辦法<br />\n鬼佬太多弱智，打機淨係玩一樣玩法嘅車槍球<br />\n調整唔到打唔同遊戲㩒唔同制<br />\n要就返佢哋"},{"pid":"19b190e967adaf452d1e79978483c84b332dd53d","tid":2381962,"uid":123926,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T06:41:13.000Z","msg":"好奇怪呢啲咁反常嘅設計,<br />\n點解亞洲區仲未有人聯署挑戰罪大霸權? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06a9e4fc99ef709751119514877fca8f98ca0a94","tid":2381962,"uid":11719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s